    <item>
      <title>自1980年代以来，加深美国债券抛售发出的收益率飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/us-treasury-selloff-is-worst-since-repo-market-chaos-in-2019</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者继续从美国资产退缩，国库的抛售加剧了，这将使更长的日期收益率朝着1980年代以来每周最大的激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/us-treasury-selloff-is-worst-since-repo-market-chaos-in-2019</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 13:55:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国的债券从来没有损失过这么多的骗局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/us-bonds-have-never-lost-out-this-much-to-german-bunds-in-a-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与德国外板相比，美国国库在数十年中的每周最糟糕的抛售方面处于正轨状态，这说明了唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税政策在多大程度上破坏了对市场最安全的资产的信念。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/us-bonds-have-never-lost-out-this-much-to-german-bunds-in-a-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 09:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易战的愤怒，欧洲股票损失第三周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/european-stocks-edge-higher-with-index-set-for-third-weekly-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国将美国商品的关税提高到125％之后，欧洲股票连续第三周下跌，这标志着两国之间的贸易战争进一步升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/european-stocks-edge-higher-with-index-set-for-third-weekly-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 07:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街动荡动荡的股票随着债券的流失：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在混乱的一周结束时，债券与美元息息相关，随着美国 - 中国贸易争端的加剧威胁到全球经济和金融体系中的动荡。股票鞭打了，而担心不断增加外国投资者正在击败美国资产的撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:39:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税混乱是赚钱的，让华尔街飞翔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/tariff-chaos-comes-for-earnings-leaves-wall-street-flying-blind</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽·谢尔（Mari Shor）深入介绍了唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税对她在哥伦比亚螺纹公司（Columbia Threadneedle）分析的数十家消费者公司的意义，当时有人中断了她。同事说，玛丽（Mari）暂停了关税，您覆盖的股票飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/tariff-chaos-comes-for-earnings-leaves-wall-street-flying-blind</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
